original_title: Wschód Kultury: Lao Che i Trio Mandili
overview: The Georgian Trio Mandili and the Polish band Lao Che perform together at Europejski Stadion Kultury 2018 in Warsaw, Poland. Trio Mandili play traditional Caucasian/Georgian folk music, while Lao Che's genre is a crossover of various styles such as ska, ambient, and folk.
title: Wschód Kultury: Lao Che i Trio Mandili
